      "parameters": {
        "width": 520,
        "height": 716,
        "content": "## Who it's for\nBusy women, creators, and homemakers who want a gentle, automated daily affirmation.\n\n## What it does\n- Runs every morning at 7 AM  \n- Picks one affirmation at random  \n- Sends via **email** (required) and **Telegram** (optional)  \n- Zero secrets stored in nodes\u2014everything is configurable\n\n## How to set up\n1. Import this workflow  \n2. Credentials \u2192 add **SMTP** (Email) and **Telegram Bot** (optional)  \n3. Open **Set: Configuration** and enter your email, Telegram chat ID (or leave empty to disable)  \n4. Edit the affirmations list  \n5. Activate\n\n## Requirements\n- SMTP credential  \n- Telegram Bot credential (optional)  \n\n## How to customize\n- Change Cron time or frequency  \n- Swap affirmations list for quotes, bible verses, etc.  \n- Add a Notion logger branch if desired"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
